data.description: The Stadium Lofts awaits you -- resort-style living! This beautifully upgraded condo offers a tremendous value and location. With 1 assigned parking space and additional storage closet this home is perfect for the a first time buyer or investor. Interior 9 ft. ceilings, and dual-pane windows throughout. Modern kitchen boasts upgraded stainless-steel appliances (gas range/oven, dishwasher, microwave). The spacious living room has lots of natural lighting from the sliding patio door with living room balcony overlooking the courtyard. Laundry is in-unit. Master bedroom features a ceiling fan and a walk-in closet. The Stadium Loft Community is complete with amenities which include a fitness center, heated pool & spa, dry sauna, conference room, game room, landscaped courtyards, and BBQ areas. Home is centrally located in Anaheim's Platinum Triangle, and minutes away from Angel Stadium, Honda Center, Disneyland, The Block at Orange, Anaheim Garden Walk, and the Amtrak station.
